                    <span>I am fairly new to the language of wooden boat building and found the book a difficult read. The book would benefit greatly from a well illustrated glossary. The illustrations redeem the more obscure text but not enough to make it a fully understandable read</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great Illustrations But!</div>
