                    <span>Since I am fairly new to the language of wooden boat building I found the terms in this book very hard to follow even with my sailing terms dictionary. The book would benefit greatly by a well illustrated glossary of terms. The illustration do make up for the rather obscure language but not enough to make it a fully understandable read.</span>
                  
              
